Al-Munawi said, \u201cMeaning, one doubts it contains the word of Allah, or indulges the debate over whether it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32670,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/seven-ahruf-do-not-argue\/","url_meta":{"origin":39236,"position":5},"title":"Hadith Ahruf: Quran revealed in seven readings, do not argue it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Juhaym reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Quran is recited in seven ways. Do not argue over the Quran, for arguing over the Quran is an act of unbelief.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 17199 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u062c\u064f\u0647\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/39236","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,